{"tid":1690420,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"要贏，就一定要做呢堆野，缺一不可！","createTime":"2019-11-03T10:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T10:32:52.000Z","uid":254210,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"88c0f7f42b68d956f151a993ad1866492515ae2e","tid":1690420,"uid":254210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:16:37.000Z","msg":"成個FB 同連登都係度日鬧夜鬧，但背後付出既有幾多？問過d 人有冇罷過工、罷買、遊行、Twitter,問完喇。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">原來個個都係做d唔做d！</span></strong></span>個效果唔會明顯，所以我整合作一個和理非行動list俾大家參考，每一日都要做，寫漏左大家幫手補上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 行動篇<br />\n<br />\n1.1 每日參與黃懲罰、藍罷買,不論係食店定係日常購物都要做，共建黃色經濟圈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用WhatsGap 、 黃藍認證，黃藍list check <br />\n<br />\n1.2 每日上twitter retweet news/FB share 港共軍政府惡行，俾埋下面條link 你，日日入去搵/task1 、/task2、/task3 <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQQy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=3840ebbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.3 日日Facebook 對唔同濕鳩page 檢舉，檢舉原因自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.4 罷睇CCTVB <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我發現好多人一邊話光復香港，一邊睇CCTVB</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.5 有合法遊行同集會都會去，屌你老母警甴10分鐘取消集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.6 花時間溫和地同戇鳩中立黨同淺藍傾計/引佢地去睇連儂牆，嘗試令佢地變色。好高難度，又要耐性，但都要做！多一個人黃，多一分力量。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.7<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">捐錢、捐物資</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.8 發動10點大叫口號，11點後就唔好了。<br />\n<br />\n2.心態篇<br />\n<br />\n2.1 絕不能割蓆，包括對一切勇武同販民都係，人地想帶風向要我地割蓆，絕不可以中計。勇武為我地犧牲咁多，用血去換自由，用血保護市民，用血反抗暴政，絕對唔可以割蓆。至於班販民政棍，都唔可以割，佢地本身有一定量社區網絡，一旦分割，唔排除反抗力量大減。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我屌你老母販民，我警告你地咪撚再割蓆！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪撚一過區選就打回原形！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.2 可以失望、但決不可以絕望，亦不可以習慣同麻木<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.3 相信希望，但唔好只依賴人權法案，一齊諗諗有咩野仲可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.4不要忘記所有暴行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我只係一個冷氣軍師，自問好多包袱做唔到勇武，只能做一個和理非，以上係現時我認為和理非仲可以做到既野，今日唔做，以後冇得做"},{"pid":"b8375ea61ce2b0d27fbd20d4ef1f948620d7ca74","tid":1690420,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:17:32.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"406de8305868c0f0fe6c91b2ea98f69f4da330c1","tid":1690420,"uid":254210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2T5AFne.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2T5AFne.jpg&h=d2776d13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r9hjnAA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr9hjnAA.jpg&h=a1861149&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MVLAFng.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMVLAFng.jpg&h=f51663f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mBY24OW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmBY24OW.jpg&h=5d4ce941&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ASPmAVC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FASPmAVC.jpg&h=4d51e9bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MRoeVVD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMRoeVVD.jpg&h=a9fb7aaf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iOUaufE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiOUaufE.jpg&h=862e9eb0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VA4JPfF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVA4JPfF.jpg&h=b03b85c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2pvUbt1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2pvUbt1.jpg&h=56560840&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WHiuKO1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWHiuKO1.jpg&h=e46e5c09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ffc1cc2a75d13f4953d63fe03e87c476f8bdc48","tid":1690420,"uid":254210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:19:40.000Z","msg":"721、831、101？<br />\n大家要記得更加多！615義士殞命，71齊上齊落立法會都要記住"},{"pid":"8448d21ade452778a9b1e5b6eb02056b0806d946","tid":1690420,"uid":254210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:19:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c6f85c27653bd58edc17974998ee4ef2ad05318","tid":1690420,"uid":254210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:21:13.000Z","msg":"行動篇漏左<br />\n<br />\n我覺得d 活動要有form,唔好太急搞"},{"pid":"846fe9e606ebfd4efcef8363f92c2f541a485974","tid":1690420,"uid":254210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:21:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa83f8a9e0c21d278708633f3083132b3620d7b7","tid":1690420,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:22:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"576207e998448508f5aaa880a28dbf20c571f856","tid":1690420,"uid":123047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:23:11.000Z","msg":"抗爭是全職的"},{"pid":"7eac44c54d398f6c6b795c818c7686636d477d10","tid":1690420,"uid":254210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:23:13.000Z","msg":"負評講下點解負評，一齊拎出黎傾，先可以做得更好"},{"pid":"7433262490ef63054b929aa1c477997004bad5f3","tid":1690420,"uid":272292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:23:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"509ab1c65e0a600bb6361c0151fd24dbe53e651a","tid":1690420,"uid":254210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:24:07.000Z","msg":"每日提一提身邊人一齊做"},{"pid":"e54941437e840c41fb42d5b19ac5